'''尼爾·夏里斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Neil Harris'''}}，{{bd|1977年|7月12日|catidx=Harris, Neil}}）是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]前[[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]，退役後擔任教練，現時執教[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]。

夏里斯就讀於[[埃塞克斯郡|埃塞克斯郡]]的布萊特伍德學校（Brentwood School），比[[法蘭·林柏特|法蘭·林柏特]]高一級。

== 生平 ==
=== 米禾爾 ===
夏里斯早期曾效力數支非聯賽球隊，直到加盟[[劍橋城足球會|劍橋城]]（Cambridge City）才真正開展其足球事業。他稍後於1998年3月26日以3萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]被賣到[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|米禾爾]]。

於1998年4月4日夏里斯首次披甲出戰[[布里斯托流浪足球俱乐部|-{布里斯托流浪}-]]。1998/99年球季，夏里斯在9月19日2-1擊敗[[北安普顿足球俱乐部|諾咸頓]]一役取得首個入球，在效力米禾爾的首個完整球季射入18球，翌季在各項比賽合共射入25球，這時已有傳言夏里斯可能會轉投[[英超|英超]]的球會<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/858683.stm |title=Lions insist Harris is staying |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2000-07-30 |accessdate=2009-01-20 }}</ref></small>。

2000/01年球季夏里斯處於巔峰狀態，2000年9月23日5-0大破[[牛津联足球俱乐部|牛津联]]夏里斯取得本季首次[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/936916.stm |title=Millwall 5-0 Oxford |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2000-09-23 |accessdate=2009-01-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307010150/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/936916.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；再分別在對[[科尔切斯特联足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:科尔切斯特;zh-hk:高車士打}-]]<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/1085922.stm |title=Millwall 6-1 Colchester |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2000-12-26 |accessdate=2009-01-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307131637/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/1085922.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>及[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/1102606.stm |title=Reading 3-4 Millwall |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2001-01-06 |accessdate=2009-01-20 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310075410/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/1102606.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>射入三球，球季結束後除以28個入球成為[[英格蘭足球聯賽|乙組〈第三級〉聯賽]]神射手，被球迷以[[第二次世界大戰|二戰]]空軍英雄亞瑟爵士（Sir Arthur Harris, 1st Baronet）的暱稱「''"Bomber" Harris''」稱之為「轟炸機」（''Bomber''）外，更協助球隊奪得聯賽冠軍<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/1310420.stm |title=Millwall clinch title |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2001-05-05 |accessdate=2009-01-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307221356/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/1310420.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，升級甲組〈第二級〉聯賽，為結束夏里斯可能會轉投[[英超|英超]]球會的傳聞，2001年5月25日米禾爾與他續約四年<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/1352038.stm |title=Harris signs new Millwall deal |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2001-05-25 |accessdate=2009-01-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307123318/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/1352038.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

夏里斯雖然在[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]出生及長大，但他的祖父是[[蘇格蘭人|蘇格蘭人]]，使他有資格代表[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭國家隊]]出賽，當時的蘇格蘭領隊克雷格·布朗（Craig Brown）更曾希望挑選他入伍<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/1141837.stm |title=Brown keen to cap Harris |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2001-01-28 |accessdate=2009-01-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307042032/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/1141837.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，初時夏里斯表示無意代表蘇格蘭，其後又說會考慮<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/1144183.stm |title=Harris in Scotland U-turn |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2001-01-30 |accessdate=2009-01-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307103314/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/1144183.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，最終不了了之，夏里斯亦無緣在國際賽場上一顯身手。

但在2001年6月夏里斯被診斷患上[[睾丸癌|睾丸癌]]<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/1368211.stm |title=Millwall striker has cancer |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2001-06-03 |accessdate=2009-01-20 |archive-date=2008-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081207162351/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/1368211.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，經歷[[手術|手術]]及兩星期[[放射線療法|放射線療]]，夏里斯在開季前恢復操練<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/1428697.stm |title=Harris to return soon |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2001-08-05 |accessdate=2009-01-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307235626/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/1428697.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，9月5日為米禾爾預備隊對[[巴尼特足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:巴尼特;zh-hk:班列特}-]]，下半場後補入替並射入一球<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/1527379.stm |title=Harris returns after cancer |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2001-09-05 |accessdate=2009-01-20 |archive-date=2013-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130630134447/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/1527379.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，更於9月18日再次披甲一隊，在下半場後補入替對[[巴恩斯利足球俱乐部|班士利]]，再於9月25日同樣後補上陣戰[[溫布頓足球會|溫布頓]]。但賽後夏里斯未能跟上大運動量的操練，惟有遵從醫生的勸解靜心休養<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/1643398.stm |title=Harris nears return |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2001-11-07 |accessdate=2009-01-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307095137/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/1643398.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。夏里斯於11月20日再次復出，為米禾爾預備隊對[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]上陣25分鐘；12月8日再為一隊上陣出戰[[谢周三足球俱乐部|錫周三]]；2002年1月2日米禾爾4-1擊敗[[沃特福德足球俱乐部|屈福特]]，夏里斯射入「埋齋」的一球，是他康復後首個入球<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/1738703.stm |title=Harris earns McGhee praise |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-01-02 |accessdate=2009-01-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307171436/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/1738703.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，2001/02年球季因病而只有4球斬獲，但煞科戰對[[格林斯比镇足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:格林斯比镇;zh-hk:甘士比}-]]夏里斯射入兩球協助球隊3-1取勝<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/1935819.stm |title=Lions see off Mariners |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-04-21 |accessdate=2009-01-23 |archive-date=2015-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150406064218/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/1935819.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，米禾爾穩守聯賽第四位取得升級季後賽的資格，但準決賽兩回合累計1-2負於最終獲得冠軍的[[伯明翰城足球俱乐部|伯明翰城]]。一年後夏里斯證實完全康復，為此夏里斯成立一個名為「尼爾·夏里斯向每人呼籲」（''Neil Harris Everyman Appeal''）的[[癌病|癌病]][[慈善|慈善]]組織<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/1668736.stm |title=Harris launches cancer appeal |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2001-11-22 |accessdate=2009-01-17 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304102622/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/1668736.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2002/03年球季，季前隊醫為夏里斯特製鞋墊以解決其跑動時脛節的問題<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/2155738.stm |title=New boots for Harris |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-07-27 |accessdate=2009-01-23 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308193554/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/2155738.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2002年9月28日作客[[考文垂足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:考文垂;zh-hk:高雲地利}-]]，下半場末段夏里斯射入一球協助球隊3-2取勝兼入本季首球<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/2272666.stm |title=Coventry 2-3 Millwall |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-09-28 |accessdate=2009-01-23 |archive-date=2003-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20031001050028/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/2272666.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。雖然米禾爾於季尾8戰6勝，但只獲聯賽第九位，未能取得升級季後賽的席位，夏里斯射入12球。

2003/04年球季，2003年10月領隊{{tsl|en|Mark McGhee|马克·麦克菲|-{zh-cn:马克·麦克菲;zh-hant:麥基爾}-}}（Mark McGhee）辭任，由[[丹尼斯·韋斯|丹尼斯·韋斯]]兼任看守領隊。本季夏里斯雖然僅射入10球，但協助球隊晉級[[英格蘭足總盃|足總盃]]決賽，於八強作客[[特兰米尔流浪者足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:特兰米尔;zh-hk:燦美爾}-]]，夏里斯與[[蒂姆·卡希尔|卡希爾]]各入一球以2-1淘汰對手<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/3508054.stm |title=Tranmere 1-2 Millwall |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-03-16 |accessdate=2009-01-23 |archive-date=2004-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040518222947/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/3508054.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，惟最終決賽以0-3負於[[曼聯|曼聯]]屈居亞軍<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/3725063.stm |title=Man Utd win FA Cup |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-05-22 |accessdate=2009-01-20 |archive-date=2016-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160112103848/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/fa_cup/3725063.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2004/05年球季，時任球員兼領隊的[[丹尼斯·韋斯|丹尼斯·韋斯]]不相信夏里斯可以回復佳態，上半季僅獲8次正選上陣機會，包括對[[费伦茨瓦罗斯TC|费伦茨瓦罗斯]]的兩場[[歐洲足協盃|歐洲足協盃]]比賽，沒有一場比賽踢足全場，僅射入1球，於2004年12月3日被外借到[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]一個月爭取上陣機會<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/4066581.stm |title=Bluebirds take Harris on loan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-12-03 |accessdate=2009-01-20 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308002848/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/4066581.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。夏里斯在卡迪夫城獲得三次上陣，最後一場作客對[[谢菲尔德联足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:谢菲尔德联;zh-hant:錫菲聯}-]]取得正選，於上半場41分鐘首開紀錄，但1分鐘後[[格拉汉姆·卡瓦纳吉|卡維拿治]]被罰離場，下半場十人應戰下反敗1-2<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/4087895.stm |title=Sheff Utd 2-1 Cardiff |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-12-18 |accessdate=2009-01-23 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310074229/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/4087895.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。夏里斯與[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]未能達成私人條件，最終被賣到剛於2004/05年球季降級到[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|甲級聯賽]]的[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|諾定咸森林]]，簽約兩年半，轉會費沒有透露<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/nottm_forest/4116061.stm |title=Forest sign Harris from Millwall |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-12-21 |accessdate=2009-01-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307143516/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/nottm_forest/4116061.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，夏里斯共為米禾爾在各項比賽上陣268場，射入98球，而單在聯賽則射入93球，與[[泰迪·舒寧咸|舒寧咸]]共同保持米禾爾聯賽最高入球紀錄。

=== 諾定咸森林 ===
夏里斯在城市球場（City Ground）卻未能正常發揮，僅獲5次正選上陣機會及沒有入球。於2005/06年球季初被外借到上年與森林一同降級的[[吉林汉姆足球俱乐部|基寧咸]]一個球季<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/g/gillingham/4192570.stm |title=Harris joins Gillingham on loan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-08-28 |accessdate=2009-01-20 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310105347/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/g/gillingham/4192570.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，在為基寧咸上陣的首場比賽對[[布伦特福德足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:布伦特福德;zh-hk:賓福特}-]]即射入一球<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/4168716.stm |title=Brentford 1-1 Gillingham |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-08-29 |accessdate=2009-01-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307173928/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/4168716.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，期間共上陣39場及射入6球，球季結束後借用期滿返回森林。

=== 米禾爾 ===

在被森林放棄後不足24小時，於2007年1月8日夏里斯重返[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|米禾爾]]，簽約18個月<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/6245625.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |title=Striker Harris returns to Lions |date=2007-01-09 |accessdate=2009-01-20 |archive-date=2013-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130626202022/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/6245625.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2007年1月20日在夏里斯為米禾爾上陣的第二場比賽對[[罗瑟勒姆足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:罗瑟勒姆;zh-hk:洛達咸}-]]，上半場16分鐘首開紀錄，除協助球隊大勝4-0外，更以94球超越與[[泰迪·舒寧咸|舒寧咸]]共同保持的球會聯賽最高入球紀錄<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6258675.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |title=Millwall 4-0 Rotherham |date=2007-01-20 |accessdate=2009-01-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307111439/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6258675.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。回歸後的半季夏里斯共有5球斬獲。 

[[2007年至2008年英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|2007/08年球季]]，夏里斯苦戰到2007年12月29日對[[克鲁足球俱乐部|克魯]]才告「開齋」<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7157332.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |title=Millwall 2-0 Crewe |date=2007-12-29 |accessdate=2009-01-21 |archive-date=2008-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080102225714/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7157332.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，更於[[元旦|元旦]]對[[北安普顿足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:北安普顿;zh-hk:諾咸頓}-]]吃了一面[[紅牌|紅牌]]<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7163900.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |title=Northampton 1-1 Millwall |date=2008-01-01 |accessdate=2009-01-21 |archive-date=2008-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080104060712/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7163900.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。直到2008年2月僅射入兩球，即將於季後約滿的夏里斯被領隊[[肯尼·杰基特|肯尼·杰基特]]（Kenny Jackett）通知將不獲提供新約，現階段他亦不在球隊首選十一人中<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/7263404.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |title=Harris told he can leave Millwall |date=2008-02-25 |accessdate=2009-01-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307160729/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/7263404.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。由於眾多球員受傷患困擾<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/7323563.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |title=Jackett hopes injuries will clear |date=2008-04-01 |accessdate=2009-01-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307135737/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/7323563.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，杰基特不得不再次起用夏里斯。米禾爾在聯賽剩餘兩輪對[[卡莱尔联足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:卡莱尔联;zh-hk:卡素爾}-]]及[[斯温登足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:斯温登;zh-hk:史雲頓}-]]的比賽必須取勝一場方可成功保級，4月26日對卡素爾一役夏里斯射入一球[[十二碼|十二碼]]及交出一次助攻，協助球隊淨勝3-0及脫離降級危機<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7358668.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |title=Millwall 3-0 Carlisle |date=2008-04-26 |accessdate=2009-01-21 |archive-date=2008-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080429102347/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7358668.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，賽後獲主場球迷起立鼓掌，而領隊杰基特亦讚許其表現出色及具有領導才能<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/7371288.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |title=Harris hopeful over Lions future |date=2008-04-28 |accessdate=2009-01-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307080835/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/7371288.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。6月4日夏里斯獲提供一年新約<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/7433026.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |title=Harris signs new Lions contract |date=2008-06-04 |accessdate=2009-01-21 |archive-date=2009-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090117113623/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/7433026.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

[[2008年至2009年英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|2008/09年球季]]夏里斯重拾佳態，季初協助米禾爾在主場取得兩連勝，2008年9月17日因神經問題需休戰一個月<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/7620961.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |title=Millwall striker Harris sidelined |date=2008-09-17 |accessdate=2009-01-21 |archive-date=2008-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080921222056/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/7620961.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。10月18日復出主場對[[利兹联足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:利兹联;zh-hk:列斯聯}-]]，夏里斯交出一次助攻及梅開二度，協助球隊反勝3-1<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7665113.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |title=Millwall 3-1 Leeds |date=2008-10-18 |accessdate=2009-01-21 |archive-date=2008-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081021054855/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7665113.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。12月13日作客2-1擊敗[[沃尔索尔足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:沃尔索尔;zh-hk:華素爾}-]]，夏里斯上半場16分鐘首開紀錄的一球，追平舒寧咸所保持111球球會歷來最高入球紀錄<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7764768.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |title=Walsall 1-2 Millwall |date=2008-12-13 |accessdate=2009-01-21 |archive-date=2009-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090112232045/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7764768.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。一個月之後的2009年1月13日，在[[英格蘭足總盃|足總盃]]第三圈重賽作客對[[克鲁足球俱乐部|克魯]]，夏里斯於下半場54分鐘離門兩碼射入反先2-1的一球，是他為米禾爾射入的第112球，打破舒寧咸所保持的球會歷來最高入球紀錄<small><ref>{{en}} {{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/7815354.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |title=Crewe 2-3 Millwall |date=2009-01-13 |accessdate=2009-01-21 |archive-date=2009-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090117234921/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/7815354.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2010年1月28日夏里斯續約至2012年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_5891159,00.html |title=Lions duo extend stays |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-01-28 |accessdate=2010-01-29 |archive-date=2010-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100131015343/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_5891159,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2010年2月夏里斯在5場聯賽轟入5球，領導米禾爾站穩升班附加賽席位，獲選為「2月份英甲最佳球員」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.football-league.co.uk/league1/news/20100306/harris-named-player-of-the-month_2248206_1985706 |title=HARRIS NAMED PLAYER OF THE MONTH |publisher=[[英格蘭足球聯賽|''football-league.co.uk'']] |date=2010-03-06 |accessdate=2010-03-07 }}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref></small>。米禾爾以第3位的成績結束球季並參加升班附加賽，於準決賽兩回合累計2-0淘汰[[哈德斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|哈德斯菲爾德]]，決賽1-0擊敗[[斯温登足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:斯温登; zh-hk:史雲頓;}-]]升班[[英冠|英冠]]。

=== 修安聯 ===
2011年6月9日夏里斯雖然與[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|米禾爾]]仍然有1年合約，但獲得領隊[[肯尼·杰基特|肯尼·杰基特]]（Kenny Jackett）放行同意提前解除合約，讓夏里斯可以免費轉投家鄉的[[英乙|英乙]]球隊[[绍森德足球俱乐部|修安聯]]，簽約三年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13714269.stm |title=Southend sign Millwall striker Neil Harris |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-06-09 |accessdate=2011-06-11 |archive-date=2011-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110610021028/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13714269.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

